<p><strong><span>8月事件驱动投资策略</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>事件驱动观点</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>主线观察：8月重点关注政策与产业主线</span></strong></p>
<p><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200807/99ec55c331e343568464954c5658c893.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
